  <refnamediv>
    <refname>clear_pixmap</refname>
    <refpurpose>erase the pixmap
  buffer</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>clear_pixmap()</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>If a graphic window <literal>pixmap</literal> property is <literal>"on"</literal>
    the drawings are send to a pixmap memory instead of the screen display.
    </para>
    <para/>
    <para>The <literal>clear_pixmap()</literal> instruction erase the pixmap, but not
    the screen.</para>
    <para/>
    <para>The pixmap mode can be used to obtain smooth animations.</para>
  </refsection>
